metadata.name: PEANUT BUTTER
metadata.description: Twenty Duce collabs with the silky smooth production of Mad Keys on this track Peanut Butter. We understand some people may have been affected by the bear market, so 100 editions will be released at an extremely affordable price in an attempt to attract current/aspiring collectors and onboard new collectors at a low barrier of entry. All collectors will receive special perks from either Artist in the future for holding the token. Thank you for building with us!
